By Henry Tyohemba, Abuja PDP Voice Worldwide has written to congratulate His Excellency Governor Godwin Obaseki and
deputy in their victory in the just concluded Edo State election, stating that the victory is a well deserved one that will bring a dynamic political turn in the Nigerian political space. This was contained in a statement issued by the political pressure group and signed by its National Chairman, Chief Victor Lamai. According to the group, the victory of Governor Obaseki at the just concluded poll confirms his uncommon leadership style that has endeared him to the good people of Edo State and has opened up a new dynamic political revolution in the state and the country. The statement also reads that, “your resounding success in the just concluded poll which is still being widely celebrated by all true lovers of democracy has sent strong political shock waves through the nation’s political landscape; as most political watchers believe and rightly so that Edo State electorates have through their affirmative choice to re-elect you has set in motion a political revolution that will show that power truly belong to the people and they shall no longer sleep on their rights to freely determines who leads them at anytime “. The group also noted that, they never regretted the role they played in mobilizing and sensitizing the good people of Edo State home and in diaspora on the need to ensure that they reelect His Excellency governor Godwin Obaseki not just as the party’s flag bearer but because of the uncommon leadership qualities he has demonstrated despite been surrounded by pseudo democrats who sought to use their influence as bargaining chip to annex the common wealth of the state for their personal use.
The PDP Voice Worldwide also extol the governor’s unwavering principles and personal values that made him side with the people of the state. “Seeking leaders in our society with such rare quality is like seeking out a needle out of a haystack. We are indeed proud to have in you a rare breed of the Nigerian political class”. The group promised to join the dynamic team of His Excellency in ensuring that his reign goes down in history as one of the most outstanding of all time both in physical and social transformation of the state. 